I don't want advice. I don't need pity. I need some kick ass ladies to drink wine with on my full week of solo vacation. 

I probably shouldn't be completely alone for the entire week. I will be near Winston Salem June 6-9 and might be down to relax at an outdoor bar and just chit chat with people. 

If you know the area let me know where good places to people watch are, and places to avoid. 

Guys, no thanks. I'm not down for revenge. I am focusing on myself, and not needing to go through STD checks again.

