width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Unlock a Treasure Chest of Audiobooks and eBooks… with Libby (and a little strategy)  

If you’re not using the Libby app yet, you’re missing out on one of the best-kept secrets for audiobook and eBook lovers.

It connects you to your library’s digital collection — for free — and works like magic on your phone, Kindle, or tablet.

But here’s something a lot of people don’t realize (I just researched this for myself):

You aren’t limited to just your local library. 

Many libraries across the country offer memberships to non-residents — sometimes free, sometimes for a small fee — and they can unlock MASSIVE audiobook and Kindle book collections through Libby.

For example:

•	I just picked up a Queens Public Library card for $50/year.
(Their audiobook and Kindle eBook collection is huge — way bigger than my local options!)
	
•	Other top libraries like Houston Public Library, Fairfax County Public Library, and Charlotte Mecklenburg Library also offer non-resident cards if you want even more options.
	
•	You can add multiple libraries to your Libby app and search across all of them at once for the books you want.

Bottom line:

If you love audiobooks, eBooks, or you just want way more choices without constantly buying new stuff — look into getting extra library cards.

A little bit of strategy can save you a ton of money and give you access to an endless stream of amazing content.

Happy reading and listening!

#Libby #Libraries #Audiobooks #Ebooks #PersonalDevelopment</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XhmdrxQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[gambrill]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Pastry Masterpieces by Magri Alberto</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Gjdd1rb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qlDBMKB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Gjdd1rb</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JasonM1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Synchronized</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GKeSuwi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5iNCZcN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GKeSuwi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JasonM1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dangerous but social.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/k5bcwtZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0QMVyXQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/k5bcwtZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shhhh.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2SHZ0Qx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2agL38x.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bJeTpTL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2SHZ0Qx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheReturnOfMadJuan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We both run on electricity</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WUT30LM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5UxsSHY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rSCItdr.gif" style